cs.CR, cs.CY, cs.SE, cs.DC, cs.NI 

This paper discusses security issues and digital forensics in relation to IoT devices, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and cybercrime (cs.CY). The paper also discusses the challenges of investigating IoT devices, which relates to software engineering (cs.SE) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). Finally, the paper discusses the integration of a large number of objects in IoT forensic interest, which falls under the category of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
